**Designing DbContext with TPH and relationships**

I'm drafting AppDbContext to use TPH for Person and Agency hierarchies with discriminators, configuring rowversion concurrency tokens, and defining key one-to-many and one-to-one relationships to ensure consistency. The DigitalWallet-ServicePortal relation will be adjusted to a one-to-many, where ServicePortal holds multiple DigitalWallets, aligning entity classes and simplifying foreign key ownership accordingly.
